                     <interp inst="t17980418-47-person368" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I was going past Mr. Bateman's, and saw a whole set of boys going backwards and forwards, and the prisoner was amongst them; I thought something was going forward, I turned round, and saw the prisoenr take the buckles out of Mr. Bateman's window.</p>
               <p>Q. You are sure as to his person? - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you know him before? - A. No; only I was in Rose-lane one day, when I heard him make use of an expression to his mother that is not fit to mention.</p>
